## Integration with CI/CD

Linear issues can be linked to commits and PRs:

```bash
# Commit format
git commit -m "fix: resolve login validation [COR-123]"

# PR title format
feat: Add Prisma v7 support [COR-123]
```

Linear automatically detects issue references and creates bidirectional links.

